description_0: A high-angle view of a light green sign in the foreground of the image with white text that reads "Respetando / el Rio". There are yellow sunflowers on the left side of the sign and white flowers on the right side of the sign. The frame of the sign is gray metal and visible on the far right side of the image. There is a tree trunk extending vertically out of view in the background on the left side of the image that is blurry and out of focus. There is a grass area visible in the background with a large number of trees taking up the majority of the background of the image. The sky is visible through the tree limbs in the top right quadrant of the image.
description_1: A daytime shot of a neighborhood yard with leaves that borders a road. The sunlight hits the yard. A silver fire hydrant frames the left side of the frame. The bottom half of a tree trunk frames the right side of the frame. Above the yard, there is a shaded road that runs left to right. Above the road, there is a house with a black metal bar fence. In the upper left of the frame, there is a large grouping of shaded trees bunched along the road.
